<xacro:include filename="$(find icart_mini_description)/urdf/sensors/hokuyo3d.urdf.xacro"/>
<xacro:sensor_hokuyo3d name="hokuyo3d" parent="base_link">
    <origin xyz="0.12 0 0.35" rpy="0 0.192 0"/>
</xacro:sensor_hokuyo3d>
-->

</robot>
